title: Has Anyone Ever Try To Sabotage Your Relationship?
itunes:title: Has Anyone Ever Try To Sabotage Your Relationship?
description:
Amara La Negra of Love & Hip-Hop talks dating, drama in the DM's, and more.  Charlamagne Tha God gives Donkey Of The Day to Jose Canseco for being jealous of A-Rod and trying to ruin his relationship.  Caller calls in emotionally and fights for his son, and says kids should not be used as leverage between the parents.
